---
title: Smoked Salmon Spread with toasted chips | Serves 2
description: Crunchy carrot sticks and toasted tortilla chips are the perfect vehicle to enjoy this colourful dip made with creme fraiche, chives and smoked salmon.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_RA_R1502_W42_IE_IEA28935-2_Main_high-81de572c.jpg
